  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Monopolar electro surgery scissors (MES), electro thermal bipolar vessel sealer (BVS) and
      ultrasonically coagulating shears (UCS) are all applied in laparoscopic colorectal surgery.
      We aimed to compare the different devices with regard to dissection time, blood loss,
      technical aspects and costs.

        -  Trial with surgical intervention
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
